    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You summon a small sphere made of earth release chakra that has a noxious odor. You then throw the sphere at a creature or object within range. Make a Ranged Ninjutsu Attack against the target. On a hit, the target takes 2d6 Earth damage and must succeed a Constitution saving throw gaining 1 rank of envenomed for 1 minute on a failed save.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and the damage by 1d6.</p>",
